\s KERA JEWE NAGANZWA N’UMUBIRI
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Kera jewe naganzwa n’umubiri, nari nafashwe mpiri n’icaha, njanwa hirya n’ino n’umuntu w’inyuma, kuko sogokuru Adamu yabinsigiye.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ubu nashitse mu Bwami bw’Imana, n’Ubwami bw’ubushobozi bwinshi, ukwiganyira n’amarira ntibishikayo, n’Ubwami bw’amahoro gusa.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Yemwe ukuntu jewe nari ngowe, nashaka gukor’iciza bikanaira, ikibi ntashaka akaba ari co nkora, jewe nari imbohe ya satani koko.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ubu nashitse mu Bwami bw’Imana, n’Ubwami bw’ubushobozi bwinshi, ukwiganyira n’amarira ntibishikayo, n’Ubwami bw’amahoro gusa.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ariko Imana ishimwe cane rwose, kuko yanyogej’ivyaha vyanje vyose, ikankura mu buja bwa satani, none ndi mu Bwami bwayo bwera.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ubu nashitse mu Bwami bw’Imana, n’Ubwami bw’ubushobozi bwinshi, ukwiganyira n’amarira ntibishikayo, n’Ubwami bw’amahoro gusa.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Icemezo c’uko Yesu yazutse, nukw’ari muzima muri jewe, yankuye mu bupfu bw’iy’isi, no mu bikorwa vyayo vy’umwiza.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ubu nashitse mu Bwami bw’Imana, n’Ubwami bw’ubushobozi bwinshi, ukwiganyira n’amarira ntibishikayo, n’Ubwami bw’amahoro gusa.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Yesu yarabishingiye intahe, ati: ni jewe Bugingo n’ukuzuka, uwunyizera ntazigera apfa nam\bd*\bd ba, none notiny’iki kandi jewe.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ubu nashitse mu Bwami bw’Imana, n’Ubwami bw’ubushobozi bwinshi, ukwiganyira n’amarira ntibishikayo, n’Ubwami bw’amahoro gusa.\bdit*
